    "content": "<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Refactoring Example</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 40px auto;\n            padding: 20px;\n            border: 1px solid #ddd;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        .header {\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        .footer {\n            text-align: right;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <h1>Refactoring Example</h1>\n        <p>This is an example of refactoring. We will refactor the code to make it cleaner and easier to maintain.</p>\n        <p>Before Refactoring:</p>\n        <pre>\n            <code>\n                var data = {\n                    \"users\": [\n                        {\"id\": 1, \"name\": \"John Doe\", \"email\": \"john@example.com\"},\n                        {\"id\": 2, \"name\": \"Jane Doe\", \"email\": \"jane@example.com\"}\n                    ]\n                };\n            </code>\n        </pre>\n        <p>After Refactoring:</p>\n        <pre>\n            <code>\n                var users = {\n                    \"id\": 1,\n                    \"name\": \"John Doe\",\n                    \"email\": \"john@example.com\"\n                };\n            </code>\n        </pre>\n        <button onclick=\"updateData()\">Update Data</button>\n        <script>\n            function updateData() {\n                var data = {\n                    \"users\": [\n                        {\"id\": 1, \"name\": \"John Doe\", \"email\": \"john@example.com\"},\n                        {\"id\": 2, \"name\": \"Jane Doe\", \"email\": \"jane@example.com\"}\n                    ]\n                };\n                document.getElementById(\"user-data\").innerHTML = JSON.stringify(data);\n            }\n        </script>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"header\">Refactoring Example</div>\n    <div class=\"footer\">Copyright 2023</div>\n</body>\n</html>"
